{"tid":2333803,"cid":8,"subCid":0,"title":"西門町小隻馬街頭徵公成功　「希望這段感情可以久一點」","createTime":"2020-12-20T17:10:54.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-21T05:27:19.000Z","uid":8307,"like":1,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"5ecd77bda252c9ec7633af800e0ec35cc41f264d","tid":2333803,"uid":8307,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-20T17:10:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://tw.appledaily.com/resizer/h6CL2XEdNZqcwAr8D_CP8k02-1M=/760x428/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/LSOZNWESPZC3DLMRLPT3NCUNVU.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2Fh6CL2XEdNZqcwAr8D_CP8k02-1M%3D%2F760x428%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FLSOZNWESPZC3DLMRLPT3NCUNVU.jpg&h=f0623c60&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n台北市西門町日前出現一名小隻女，身穿搶眼的蘿莉服，一旁放著「路邊徵友」的牌子，被網友po網後引發熱議，這名爆紅的小隻女倪安如今成功找到男友，她在IG發文表示「已經有對象了」。<br />\n<br />\n倪安在街頭徵友引發熱議，又在《批踢踢實業坊》以「台北徵公」為題發文，<span class=\"red\">表示自己23歲，身高156公分，體重50公斤左右，非常珍惜另一半，但不要被她外表所騙，</span>她內心其實是「真性情女漢子」，她笑說「跌倒會罵幹，不會嬌滴滴，但內心小女人，可接受大男人，會保護我佳。」<br />\n<br />\n倪安對於男友的條件則是「<span class=\"red\">身高172以上，BMI正常不要過胖，帥一點好至少不要醜，不需要有錢，不需高學歷，肯一起努力就好。</span>」她並強調「不要渣男，愛愛還搞偷拍」，並表示自己是認真的，希望找有結婚意願的對象。<br />\n全文:<br />\n<a href=\"https://tw.appledaily.com/life/20201220/53HMJLS6BFHWNNU42XNKTQLCNQ/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Flife%2F20201220%2F53HMJLS6BFHWNNU42XNKTQLCNQ%2F&d=10CjJG2g6dwwFxaVJa0PIXfp3ZHOIdf2SFoQnphXrww%3D&h=ee8005ec\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Flife%2F20201220%2F53HMJLS6BFHWNNU42XNKTQLCNQ%2F&h=49b6176a\" target=\"_blank\">https://tw.appledaily.com/life/20201220/53HMJLS6BFHWNNU42XNKTQLCNQ/</a>"},{"pid":"91c77576002e890a83fbef536295f1b3e1916cca","tid":2333803,"uid":38904,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-20T17:13:38.000Z","msg":"她內心其實是「真性情女漢子」<br />\n<br />\n重諗住有偽娘睇<img src=\"